### 1. Create/Get Anonymous Cart
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/carts
Accept: application/json

> {% client.global.set("cartId", response.body.data.id); client.global.set("cartToken", response.body.data.accessToken); %}

### 2. Add Item to Cart
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/carts/{{cartId}}/items
X-Cart-Token: {{cartToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "variantId": "REPLACE_WITH_VARIANT_ID",
  "quantity": 1
}

### 3. Get Cart Detail
GET {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/carts/{{cartId}}
X-Cart-Token: {{cartToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Update Item Quantity
PATCH {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/carts/{{cartId}}/items/REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID
X-Cart-Token: {{cartToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 2
}

### 5. Remove Item from Cart
DELETE {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/carts/{{cartId}}/items/REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID
X-Cart-Token: {{cartToken}}
